    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 32-35.</p><p>Note of Rebuttal</p><p>Also at 21st level, your knowledge of the arcane has given you considerable insight into how to control the enemy. When a creature within 60 feet of you casts a spell or makes an attack, you can use your reaction and expend 1 Legendary Point to perform a Note of Rebuttal. If the creature is casting a spell, you cast Counterspell at 7th level without expending a spell slot. If the creature is making an attack, you speak a word of power that overwhelms the mind, interrupting the attack.</p></div>",
